latestPosts.caption:
It’s finally here! I’m SO THRILLED to share our official key art for @universalorlando’s #EpicUniverse! To be a part of a major theme park’s beginnings is something I never imagined I could be a part of and it’s a dream come true to bring together so many iconic characters and worlds onto one EPIC poster. 🌌

I’m incredibly fortunate to have collaborated with @evand073, @justheidys, Azia, and the entire team on this remarkable project and I’m forever grateful for the time I spent working with such talented individuals. I love contributing to the Universal story when and where I have the opportunity to do so! ✨

Tickets are available now!

latestPosts.caption:
Happy #JurassicWorldRebirth release day! It was surreal to work on these premiere posters for each stop on the global tour for the film. Each postcard poster features a different species of dinosaur and landmarks from each country we premiered in! 

Always an absolute privilege to work with the stellar digital marketing team at @universalpictures on a franchise that I know and love very much. 

A HUGE thank you to @jp.fukumae and his incredible team for trusting me with these. Thank you to @amblin and more for sharing across your social channels as well. Seeing these posters in the hands of fans and signed by talent at premieres across the globe is honestly a dream come true! Thank you to everyone on here for all of your kind messages and comments!

latestPosts.caption:
One of the best nights of my life! Seeing the cast and crew signing our posters is a dream come true! 

Incredible video @jonbrandoncruz, @andrew_sandler and crew!

Jurassic World Rebirth director Gareth Edwards pulled off something incredible in such a short time — stunning visuals, gripping sequences, and paired with @dgkoepp’s sharp script, this film delivers. It was an absolute blast chatting with Gareth, especially discovering his love for designing movie posters (just like me!). I’ve always admired his work — Rogue One is one of my favorites — and he couldn’t have been more kind or generous. Cheers to you Gareth! 🥂
